                            A standard hood cleaning typically takes 2-4 hours, depending on the size of your system and how much buildup has accumulated. We work efficiently to minimize disruption to your business. For larger commercial systems or heavily soiled hoods, the process may take longer. We always provide an estimated timeframe when scheduling your service, and our team works diligently to complete the job as quickly as possible without compromising on quality. We're happy to schedule cleanings during your off-hours if that works better for your operation.
