                        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                            Neglecting regular hood cleaning can lead to serious consequences: increased fire hazard (grease buildup is highly flammable), failed health inspections, reduced ventilation efficiency, unpleasant odors, pest problems, and potential legal liability. The buildup can also damage your equipment and shorten its lifespan. Most importantly, a dirty hood system poses a serious fire risk to your restaurant and staff. Regular professional cleaning is not just a maintenance task—it's a critical safety and compliance requirement. Our service ensures your hood system operates safely and efficiently while keeping you compliant with all health and fire codes.
                        </p>
